dataJson.description: Real time tracking of air traffic. Work still in progress
dataJson.name: Air traffic tracker
dataJson.story: An app I am building to learn about geo-location and maps in general. In it's final form it will track in real time air trafic around a point with a given radius. At this stage it show in in rather raw format info about the aircraft, cuurent location on the map, as well as destination and origin drawn on the mapWork is still in progress
